  <brief_title>Proof of Concept Study to Determine the Safety and Antiviral Effect of BZF961 With or Without Ritonavir Boosting in Hepatitis C Virus Infected Patients</brief_title>
  <acronym>CBZF961X2201</acronym>
  <official_title>Double-blind, Randomized, Placebo-controlled, Multi-center Trial to Determine the Safety and Antiviral Effect of 3 Days of BZF961 With or Without Ritonavir Boosting in Hepatitis C Virus (HCV) Infected Patients</official_title>
