  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To evaluate the antiviral activity of 3 days of BZF961. To determine safety and tolerability
      of BZF961 in HCV patients. To evaluate pharmacokinetics of BZF961 in HCV patients.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
